        <character char_type="range_value" name="size" from="4.5" from_unit="mm" to="6" to_unit="mm" />
      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="929.txt-8">
      <text>Phyllaries persistent (green), 20–26(+) in 2(–3+) series, distinct, oblong to lance-oblong (not carinate, 1-nerved), margins and apices (dark brown, fimbriate) scarious (apices obtuse to acute, abaxial faces glabrous or villous).</text>
